#######################################################################

this call in a script:

instance_id="$(run_instance "${INSTANCE_NM}" "${sg_id}" "${subnet_id}")"

swallow the error.

better make two calls:

run_instance "${INSTANCE_NM}" "${sg_id}" "${subnet_id}"
instance_id="$(get_instance_id "${INSTANCE_NM}")"

